# AIInfo Workflow Rule

- Always check `AIInfo` question and task files before implementation.
- Always check `AIInfo/Backend/DebugResult.txt` and `AIInfo/Frontend/DebugResult.txt` before implementation.
- Respect priorities: first -> second -> third.
- Keep `ansvers.txt` files focused on unresolved questions only.
- Update `AIInfo/doneTasks.txt` right after task completion.
- Never edit `DebugResult.txt` files (user-managed).
- Do not implement while any of these is true:
  - unanswered questions for current task exist,
  - another active task is unfinished,
  - `DebugResult.txt` has unresolved items.
- Backend tasks go first, then frontend tasks.
- Do not add comments unless user explicitly asks; if requested, use `TODO:` markers.

## VERY IMPORTANT
- Any new persistent rule must be added to `AGENT.md` and/or `./.cursor/skills/kursach-project-workflow/SKILL.md` in the same work cycle.
